{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-whitelist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-no-vendor-prefix/","description":"media-feature-name-value-whitelist 指定允许的媒体功能名和值对的白名单。 此规则忽略范围和布尔上下文中的媒体功能。 选项 如果在对象中找到媒体功能名称，则仅允许其列入白名单的值。如果对象中未包含媒体功能名称，则什么都可以。 如果名称或值被 /…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"media-feature-name-value-whitelist\"><a href=\"#media-feature-name-value-whitelist\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>media-feature-name-value-whitelist</h1>\n<p>指定允许的媒体功能名和值对的白名单。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">768px</span>) {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**                ↑          ↑\n *    这些功能和值 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则忽略范围和布尔上下文中的媒体功能。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"unprefixed-media-feature-name\"</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"array\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"of\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"values\"</span>],\n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/unprefixed-media-feature-name/\"</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/regex/\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"non-regex\"</span>, /real-regex/]\n}</code></pre>\n<p>如果在对象中找到媒体功能名称，则仅允许其列入白名单的值。如果对象中未包含媒体功能名称，则什么都可以。</p>\n<p>如果名称或值被 <code>/</code> 包围（例如 <code>\"/width$/\"</code>），则它被解释为正则表达式。例如 <code>/width$/</code> 将匹配 <code>max-width</code> 和 <code>min-width</code>。</p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-json\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"min-width\"</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"768px\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"1024px\"</span>],\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"/resolution/\"</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/dpcm$/\"</span>]\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000px</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-resolution: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2dpi</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">768px</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1024px</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (orientation: portrait) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (min-resolution: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2dpcm</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (resolution: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10dpcm</span>) {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-value-whitelist.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-value-whitelist/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-value-whitelist/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-value-whitelist/index.html.d8b7cb5a73ee5a9fff0e1bdd397a808c.json"}